OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSpring Statement: Borrowing
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffigures give Rishi Sunak   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F'wiggle room'              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The chancellor has "wiggle room" to    
OL,6, help tackle the rising cost of living, 
OL,7, an influential economist has said.     
OL,9,FSir Charlie Bean told the BBC that     
OL,10,FRishi Sunak may have as much as #50bn  
OL,11,F"to play with", ahead of the Spring    
OL,12,FStatement on Wednesday.                
OL,14,FNew official data also show that the   
OL,15,Fgovernment is borrowing less than      
OL,16,Fexpected so far this year.             
OL,18,FIt comes as pressure mounts on         
OL,19,FChancellor Rishi Sunak to take action  
OL,20,Fto tackle soaring costs.               
